1.0 Whom does the policy cover?
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
The holder of a valid MasterCard Business Platinum card issued by
&BANKNAVN., as well as his/her spouse/life partner who is travelling with
him/her:
.of 5mm
*¤The cardholder's partner must live at the same address as the cardholder
to be included in the coverage.
.of 5mm
*¤The cardholder's spouse is covered, even though he/she may not live at
the same address as the cardholder.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
Any children of the cardholder and his/her spouse/partner are covered
according to the following rules, when such children are travelling
together with the cardholder:
.of 5mm
*¤Children of the cardholder and his/her spouse/partner are covered up
until the age of 21, irrespective of their address.
.of
.of 5mm
*¤Children of the cardholder and his/her spouse/partner are covered when
said children share the same address as the cardholder, irrespective of
their age.
.of
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
In this context, 'life partner' is taken to mean a person who lives
with the cardholder in a marriage-like relationship, and who, for at
least six months prior to the insurance event, has shared an address
with the cardholder.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
1.1 The insurance coverage also applies if the cardholder has a MasterCard
Business Platinum card and lives abroad.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
3.3 In the event that the duration of the journey exceeds 60 days on
account of ongoing medial treatment, coverage for illness and repatriation
shall remain in effect until the insured is discharged from medical care or
repatriated.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
3.4 In the event that the duration of the journey exceeds 60 days on
account of an unavoidably delayed return, the coverage will be
automatically extended for 48 hours.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
3.5 The insurance will apply irrespective of whether the travel was paid
with MasterCard.
.sp 5mm
