5.0 General exceptions
:SKRSLUT.
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
The insurance does not cover:
.of 5mm
*¤claims which, irrespective of the state or soundness of mind of the
insured:
.of
.of 10mm
¤*¤are caused intentionally by the policy holder/the insured
.of
.of 10mm
¤*¤are attributable to the insured being under the influence of
spirits, narcotics or other toxins, unless it can be proved that the
claim is unrelated to same
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims attributable to strikes or lockouts
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims resulting from seizure of goods, confiscation, impoundment or
other forms of intervention by the public authorities
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims arising from participation in expeditions and journeys of
discovery
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims arising from participation by the insured in criminal acts
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims attributable to nuclear leaks or nuclear detonations
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims arising from entry into a country experiencing war, war-like
conditions, violation of neutrality, civil war, insurrection or
civil unrest, terrorist activities, a military state of
emergency, revolution, epidemic, natural disaster or similar conditions
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims arising from entry into a region to which the Ministry of Foreign
Affairs of Denmark has discouraged travel
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims arising from participation in professional sport; however, the
policy does cover transport to and from the destination, and
accommodation during the stay for the insured as a private individual.
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
¤In this context, 'professional sport' is defined as sport for whose
performance the player receives payment over and above coverage of
expenses and which must therefore be declared as income.
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims arising from participation in motor races of any kind
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤the consequences of an accident that affects the insured as the driver of
or passenger on a motorcycle or a scooter/moped
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤insurance events caused by the bankruptcy of a public carrier
.of
.kp off
.kp on
