travel insurance schemes (irrespective of whether the expenses may
only be partially refunded by the Danish public travel insurance
scheme)
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤claims attributable to the insured being a crew member for an
airline, shipping line, offshore company etc. The insurance
does, however, cover transport to and from the place of work as
a crew member. A special regulation for persons who work on
offshore drilling rigs is that the insurance only covers said
persons up to the time they board the means of transport that
is to convey them to the drilling rig. Coverage recommences
once said persons exit the means of transport on returning to
dry land.
.of
