.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
*¤for treatment and accommodation abroad if the SOS International
doctor has decided - and the attending physician has agreed - that
treatment can be deferred until the insured has returned to Denmark
.of
.kp off
.kp on
.of 5mm
